            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the the beef is cooked, divide the <strong>spiced beef mixture</strong> between the <strong>crispy tortillas</strong> and spread thinly – these are your <strong>Turkish-style beef lahmacuns</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
