      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, top each <strong>Turkish-style beef lahmacun</strong> with the <strong>quick-pickled red onion</strong>, <strong>chopped tomato </strong>and a dollop of <strong>garlic yoghurt</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>salad </strong>to the side and drizzle with a little <strong>olive oil</strong> and the <strong>reserved pickling liquid</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
